## Game Mechanics Flow
1. Enemy spawns at path start, moves along path at 100px/s
2. Tower detects enemy when it enters 200px range
3. Tower shoots projectile every 1 second while enemy in range
4. Projectile homes to enemy at 300px/s
5. On hit, enemy takes 50 damage
6. Enemy dies after 2 hits (100 HP / 50 damage)

## Known Limitations/TODOs
- Only one enemy spawned at game start
- No wave/spawn system
- No resource/economy system
- Tower placement is hardcoded (not player-controlled)
- No UI (health bars, score, currency)
- Path is simple straight line
- No different enemy/tower types
- No game over/win conditions
- Projectiles have no visual representation (invisible)
- No sound effects or music

## Technical Notes
